-! # how to errors: 001-comments-block-unterminated.zo
-!
-! @cmd: `zo build 001-comments-block-unterminated.zo`
-!
-! Block comments in zo start with `-*` and end with `*-`.
-! If you forget to close one, the compiler eats everything
-! after it — your entire program disappears into the comment.

-* this block comment never closes
fun main() {}

-- EXPECTED OUTPUT:
-- [E0002] Error: Unterminated block comment
--     ╭─[ 001-comments-block-unterminated.zo:9:1 ]
--     │
--   9 │ ╭─▶ -* this block comment never closes
--     ┆ ┆
--  21 │ ├─▶ -- ────╯
--     │ │
--     │ ╰────────────── here
-- ────╯
